## OAuth endpoints

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/.well-known/oauth-authorization-server` | GET | Server metadata (discovery document) |
| `/oauth/authorize` | GET | Authorization endpoint — initiates PKCE flow, returns authorization code |
| `/oauth/token` | POST | Token endpoint — exchanges code for access/refresh tokens, or refreshes |
| `/oauth/jwks` | GET | JSON Web Key Set — public keys for verifying access tokens |
| `/oauth/revoke` | POST | Token revocation |

These are mounted directly on Express, not through the Thunderstorm API handler system.

