| Artifact | Convention |
|----------|-----------|
| Backend server module | `ModuleBE_OAuthServer` |
| Backend module pack | `ModulePackBE_OAuth` |
| API type | `API_OAuth` |
| API def constant | `ApiDef_OAuth` |
| Client entity | `DB_OAuthClient` |
| Grant entity | `DB_OAuthGrant` |
| Token entity | `DB_OAuthToken` |
| Token claims type | `OAuthTokenClaims` |
| Server metadata type | `OAuthServerMetadata` |

